		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><strong>edit: see note below</strong> <br /><br />Larger than 64 bytes? Sounds like a job for a lookup table.<br />01 0F 01 02 03 04 05 06 09 0a 0b 0c 0F 0c 0f 0f<br />11 01 11 12 13 14 15 16 19 1a 1b 1c 0c 1c 0f 0f<br />21 11 21 22 23 24 25 26 29 2a 2b 2c 1c 2c 0f 0f<br />31 21 31 32 33 34 35 36 39 3a 3b 3c 2c 3c 0f 0f<br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">My table is for hue-then-value (though all in the same process).</div> Which isn't the same thing as is being done, so…oh well. Maybe I can use it later.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
